Brief
    This is a home made extension/addon to Google Chrome, Firefox and Opera.
    It allows in one click to check the weather situation in Sweden/Nordic region.
    The weather information is provided by Swedish Meteorological and Hydrological
    Institute (SMHI, http://www.smhi.se).

    Check demo sub folder for the extension's screenshots.

Installation
    Drag and drop a .CRX (Chrome), .XPI (Firefox) or .OEX (Opera) file to your
    browser to install it. Please note that you can change your region in a
    Options page (not working for Firefox).

Copyright
    This extension is free and could be freely modified for personal needs.
    
    Extension is using scripts and resources from http://www.smhi.se. 
